Push Notifications
Get push notifications right when when Minneapolis or Saint Paul
 declares a snow emergency, and get reminders each time you have to move
 your car.
Know Where to Park
A visual diagram shows you where to park (and where
not
to park) during a snow emergency. Check the app anytime to see when you have to move your car.
Useful Information
Tap anywhere on the street diagram to read the parking rules as 
defined by the City of Minneapolis or the City of Saint Paul. Follow 
these rules and don't get towed!
Snow Alerts
was crafted for the good people of the Twin Cities by
Bust Out
.